{
  "video_id": "cXQrbxD9_Ng",
  "title": "What will future jobs look like? | Andrew McAfee",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12328.0,
      "end_time": 15277.0,
      "text": "The writer George Eliot cautioned us that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15277.0,
      "end_time": 17344.0,
      "text": "among all forms of mistake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17344.0,
      "end_time": 19707.0,
      "text": "prophecy is the most gratuitous."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19707.0,
      "end_time": 21555.0,
      "text": "The person that we would all acknowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21555.0,
      "end_time": 25857.0,
      "text": "as her 20th-century counterpart, Yogi Berra, agreed."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25857.0,
      "end_time": 27722.0,
      "text": "He said, \"It's tough to make predictions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27722.0,
      "end_time": 30458.0,
      "text": "especially about the future.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30458.0,
      "end_time": 32269.0,
      "text": "I'm going to ignore their cautions"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32269.0,
      "end_time": 34242.0,
      "text": "and make one very specific forecast."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34242.0,
      "end_time": 36882.0,
      "text": "In the world that we are creating very quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36882.0,
      "end_time": 38595.0,
      "text": "we're going to see more and more things"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38595.0,
      "end_time": 40320.0,
      "text": "that look like science fiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40320.0,
      "end_time": 43436.0,
      "text": "and fewer and fewer things that look like jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43436.0,
      "end_time": 46188.0,
      "text": "Our cars are very quickly going to start driving themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46188.0,
      "end_time": 48884.0,
      "text": "which means we're going to need fewer truck drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48884.0,
      "end_time": 51005.0,
      "text": "We're going to hook Siri up to Watson"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51005.0,
      "end_time": 53602.0,
      "text": "and use that to automate a lot of the work"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53602.0,
      "end_time": 55828.0,
      "text": "that's currently done by customer service reps"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55828.0,
      "end_time": 58732.0,
      "text": "and troubleshooters and diagnosers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58732.0,
      "end_time": 60988.0,
      "text": "and we're already taking R2D2,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60988.0,
      "end_time": 64228.0,
      "text": "painting him orange, and putting him to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64227.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66777.0,
      "text": "carrying shelves around warehouses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66777.0,
      "end_time": 68852.0,
      "text": "which means we need a lot fewer people"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68852.0,
      "end_time": 70818.0,
      "text": "to be walking up and down those aisles."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70818.0,
      "end_time": 74620.0,
      "text": "Now, for about 200 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74620.0,
      "end_time": 76803.0,
      "text": "people have been saying exactly what I'm telling you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76803.0,
      "end_time": 79620.0,
      "text": "the age of technological unemployment is at hand â€”"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79620.0,
      "end_time": 82035.0,
      "text": "starting with the Luddites smashing looms in Britain"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82035.0,
      "end_time": 83931.0,
      "text": "just about two centuries ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83931.0,
      "end_time": 85963.0,
      "text": "and they have been wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85963.0,
      "end_time": 88780.0,
      "text": "Our economies in the developed world have coasted along"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88780.0,
      "end_time": 90714.0,
      "text": "on something pretty close to full employment."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90714.0,
      "end_time": 92813.0,
      "text": "Which brings up a critical question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92813.0,
      "end_time": 95739.0,
      "text": "Why is this time different, if it really is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95739.0,
      "end_time": 98735.0,
      "text": "The reason it's different is that, just in the past few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98735.0,
      "end_time": 100630.0,
      "text": "our machines have started demonstrating skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100630.0,
      "end_time": 103255.0,
      "text": "they have never, ever had before:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103255.0,
      "end_time": 106515.0,
      "text": "understanding, speaking, hearing, seeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106515.0,
      "end_time": 110728.0,
      "text": "answering, writing, and they're still acquiring new skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110728.0,
      "end_time": 113298.0,
      "text": "For example, mobile humanoid robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113298.0,
      "end_time": 115245.0,
      "text": "are still incredibly primitive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115245.0,
      "end_time": 117083.0,
      "text": "but the research arm of the Defense Department"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117083.0,
      "end_time": 118598.0,
      "text": "just launched a competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 118598.0,
      "end_time": 120912.0,
      "text": "to have them do things like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120912.0,
      "end_time": 122645.0,
      "text": "and if the track record is any guide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122645.0,
      "end_time": 125044.0,
      "text": "this competition is going to be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 125044.0,
      "end_time": 128680.0,
      "text": "So when I look around, I think the day is not too far off at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128680.0,
      "end_time": 130856.0,
      "text": "when we're going to have androids"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130856.0,
      "end_time": 133737.0,
      "text": "doing a lot of the work that we are doing right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133737.0,
      "end_time": 137495.0,
      "text": "And we're creating a world where there is going to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137495.0,
      "end_time": 141180.0,
      "text": "more and more technology and fewer and fewer jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 141180.0,
      "end_time": 143429.0,
      "text": "It's a world that Erik Brynjolfsson and I are calling"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 143429.0,
      "end_time": 144920.0,
      "text": "\"the new machine age.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144920.0,
      "end_time": 147053.0,
      "text": "The thing to keep in mind is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 147053.0,
      "end_time": 149602.0,
      "text": "this is absolutely great news."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 149602.0,
      "end_time": 152919.0,
      "text": "This is the best economic news on the planet these days."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152919.0,
      "end_time": 156448.0,
      "text": "Not that there's a lot of competition, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156448.0,
      "end_time": 158347.0,
      "text": "This is the best economic news we have these days"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 158347.0,
      "end_time": 159963.0,
      "text": "for two main reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159963.0,
      "end_time": 162948.0,
      "text": "The first is, technological progress is what allows us"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162948.0,
      "end_time": 166685.0,
      "text": "to continue this amazing recent run that we're on"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 166685.0,
      "end_time": 169206.0,
      "text": "where output goes up over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169206.0,
      "end_time": 172532.0,
      "text": "while at the same time, prices go down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172532.0,
      "end_time": 176736.0,
      "text": "and volume and quality just continue to explode."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 176736.0,
      "end_time": 178737.0,
      "text": "Now, some people look at this and talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178737.0,
      "end_time": 180143.0,
      "text": "shallow materialism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 180143.0,
      "end_time": 182561.0,
      "text": "but that's absolutely the wrong way to look at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 182561.0,
      "end_time": 185056.0,
      "text": "This is abundance, which is exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185056.0,
      "end_time": 188478.0,
      "text": "what we want our economic system to provide."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188478.0,
      "end_time": 191694.0,
      "text": "The second reason that the new machine age"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 191694.0,
      "end_time": 194000.0,
      "text": "is such great news is that, once the androids"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 194000.0,
      "end_time": 197252.0,
      "text": "start doing jobs, we don't have to do them anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 197252.0,
      "end_time": 201008.0,
      "text": "and we get freed up from drudgery and toil."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 201008.0,
      "end_time": 203032.0,
      "text": "Now, when I talk about this with my friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 203032.0,
      "end_time": 205584.0,
      "text": "in Cambridge and Silicon Valley, they say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 205584.0,
      "end_time": 207857.0,
      "text": "\"Fantastic. No more drudgery, no more toil."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 207857.0,
      "end_time": 209908.0,
      "text": "This gives us the chance to imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 209908.0,
      "end_time": 212201.0,
      "text": "an entirely different kind of society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 212201.0,
      "end_time": 215113.0,
      "text": "a society where the creators and the discoverers"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 215113.0,
      "end_time": 216942.0,
      "text": "and the performers and the innovators"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216942.0,
      "end_time": 220451.0,
      "text": "come together with their patrons and their financiers"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 220451.0,
      "end_time": 223130.0,
      "text": "to talk about issues, entertain, enlighten,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 223130.0,
      "end_time": 225208.0,
      "text": "provoke each other.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 225208.0,
      "end_time": 229783.0,
      "text": "It's a society really, that looks a lot like the TED Conference."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 229783.0,
      "end_time": 232266.0,
      "text": "And there's actually a huge amount of truth here."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 232266.0,
      "end_time": 235289.0,
      "text": "We are seeing an amazing flourishing taking place."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 235289.0,
      "end_time": 237291.0,
      "text": "In a world where it is just about as easy"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 237291.0,
      "end_time": 240698.0,
      "text": "to generate an object as it is to print a document,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 240698.0,
      "end_time": 242787.0,
      "text": "we have amazing new possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 242787.0,
      "end_time": 246464.0,
      "text": "The people who used to be craftsmen and hobbyists"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 246464.0,
      "end_time": 248331.0,
      "text": "are now makers, and they're responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 248331.0,
      "end_time": 250721.0,
      "text": "for massive amounts of innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 250721.0,
      "end_time": 253003.0,
      "text": "And artists who were formerly constrained"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 253003.0,
      "end_time": 256171.0,
      "text": "can now do things that were never, ever possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 256171.0,
      "end_time": 258067.0,
      "text": "for them before."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 258067.0,
      "end_time": 260184.0,
      "text": "So this is a time of great flourishing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 260184.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263116.0,
      "text": "and the more I look around, the more convinced I become"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 263116.0,
      "end_time": 266190.0,
      "text": "that this quote, from the physicist Freeman Dyson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 266190.0,
      "end_time": 268223.0,
      "text": "is not hyperbolic at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 268223.0,
      "end_time": 271013.0,
      "text": "This is just a plain statement of the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 271013.0,
      "end_time": 272858.0,
      "text": "We are in the middle of an astonishing period."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 272858.0,
      "end_time": 273742.0,
      "text": "[\"Technology is a gift of God. After the gift of life it is perhaps the greatest of God's gifts. It is the mother of civilizations, of arts and of sciences.\" â€” Freeman Dyson]"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 273742.0,
      "end_time": 276533.0,
      "text": "Which brings up another great question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 276533.0,
      "end_time": 279509.0,
      "text": "What could possibly go wrong in this new machine age?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 279509.0,
      "end_time": 282871.0,
      "text": "Right? Great, hang up, flourish, go home."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 282871.0,
      "end_time": 285537.0,
      "text": "We're going to face two really thorny sets of challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 285537.0,
      "end_time": 288330.0,
      "text": "as we head deeper into the future that we're creating."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288330.0,
      "end_time": 291580.0,
      "text": "The first are economic, and they're really nicely summarized"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291580.0,
      "end_time": 294670.0,
      "text": "in an apocryphal story about a back-and-forth"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294670.0,
      "end_time": 297712.0,
      "text": "between Henry Ford II and Walter Reuther,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 297712.0,
      "end_time": 300457.0,
      "text": "who was the head of the auto workers union."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 300457.0,
      "end_time": 302640.0,
      "text": "They were touring one of the new modern factories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 302640.0,
      "end_time": 305390.0,
      "text": "and Ford playfully turns to Reuther and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 305390.0,
      "end_time": 307552.0,
      "text": "\"Hey Walter, how are you going to get these robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 307552.0,
      "end_time": 309366.0,
      "text": "to pay union dues?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 309366.0,
      "end_time": 311311.0,
      "text": "And Reuther shoots back, \"Hey Henry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 311311.0,
      "end_time": 315853.0,
      "text": "how are you going to get them to buy cars?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315853.0,
      "end_time": 318864.0,
      "text": "Reuther's problem in that anecdote"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318864.0,
      "end_time": 322973.0,
      "text": "is that it is tough to offer your labor to an economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 322973.0,
      "end_time": 324608.0,
      "text": "that's full of machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324608.0,
      "end_time": 326832.0,
      "text": "and we see this very clearly in the statistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 326832.0,
      "end_time": 329224.0,
      "text": "If you look over the past couple decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 329224.0,
      "end_time": 332888.0,
      "text": "at the returns to capital -- in other words, corporate profits --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 332888.0,
      "end_time": 334572.0,
      "text": "we see them going up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 334572.0,
      "end_time": 336659.0,
      "text": "and we see that they're now at an all-time high."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 336659.0,
      "end_time": 339360.0,
      "text": "If we look at the returns to labor, in other words"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 339360.0,
      "end_time": 341244.0,
      "text": "total wages paid out in the economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 341244.0,
      "end_time": 343791.0,
      "text": "we see them at an all-time low"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343791.0,
      "end_time": 346856.0,
      "text": "and heading very quickly in the opposite direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 346856.0,
      "end_time": 348626.0,
      "text": "So this is clearly bad news for Reuther."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 348626.0,
      "end_time": 352024.0,
      "text": "It looks like it might be great news for Ford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 352024.0,
      "end_time": 354328.0,
      "text": "but it's actually not. If you want to sell"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 354328.0,
      "end_time": 357672.0,
      "text": "huge volumes of somewhat expensive goods to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 357672.0,
      "end_time": 361460.0,
      "text": "you really want a large, stable, prosperous middle class."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 361460.0,
      "end_time": 363684.0,
      "text": "We have had one of those in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 363684.0,
      "end_time": 366317.0,
      "text": "for just about the entire postwar period."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 366317.0,
      "end_time": 370669.0,
      "text": "But the middle class is clearly under huge threat right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 370669.0,
      "end_time": 372080.0,
      "text": "We all know a lot of the statistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 372080.0,
      "end_time": 374439.0,
      "text": "but just to repeat one of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 374439.0,
      "end_time": 377206.0,
      "text": "median income in America has actually gone down"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 377206.0,
      "end_time": 378897.0,
      "text": "over the past 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 378897.0,
      "end_time": 380612.0,
      "text": "and we're in danger of getting trapped"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 380612.0,
      "end_time": 384537.0,
      "text": "in some vicious cycle where inequality and polarization"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 384537.0,
      "end_time": 387717.0,
      "text": "continue to go up over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 387717.0,
      "end_time": 390116.0,
      "text": "The societal challenges that come along"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 390116.0,
      "end_time": 392692.0,
      "text": "with that kind of inequality deserve some attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 392692.0,
      "end_time": 394360.0,
      "text": "There are a set of societal challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 394360.0,
      "end_time": 396304.0,
      "text": "that I'm actually not that worried about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 396304.0,
      "end_time": 398655.0,
      "text": "and they're captured by images like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 398655.0,
      "end_time": 400477.0,
      "text": "This is not the kind of societal problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 400477.0,
      "end_time": 402941.0,
      "text": "that I am concerned about."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 402941.0,
      "end_time": 405084.0,
      "text": "There is no shortage of dystopian visions"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 405084.0,
      "end_time": 408567.0,
      "text": "about what happens when our machines become self-aware,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 408567.0,
      "end_time": 411743.0,
      "text": "and they decide to rise up and coordinate attacks against us."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 411743.0,
      "end_time": 413490.0,
      "text": "I'm going to start worrying about those"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 413490.0,
      "end_time": 416719.0,
      "text": "the day my computer becomes aware of my printer."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 416719.0,
      "end_time": 420348.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 420348.0,
      "end_time": 423320.0,
      "text": "So this is not the set of challenges we really need to worry about."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 423320.0,
      "end_time": 426108.0,
      "text": "To tell you the kinds of societal challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 426108.0,
      "end_time": 428320.0,
      "text": "that are going to come up in the new machine age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 428320.0,
      "end_time": 432031.0,
      "text": "I want to tell a story about two stereotypical American workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 432031.0,
      "end_time": 433799.0,
      "text": "And to make them really stereotypical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 433799.0,
      "end_time": 435946.0,
      "text": "let's make them both white guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 435946.0,
      "end_time": 439708.0,
      "text": "And the first one is a college-educated"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 439708.0,
      "end_time": 442854.0,
      "text": "professional, creative type, manager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 442854.0,
      "end_time": 445605.0,
      "text": "engineer, doctor, lawyer, that kind of worker."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 445605.0,
      "end_time": 448024.0,
      "text": "We're going to call him \"Ted.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 448024.0,
      "end_time": 450297.0,
      "text": "He's at the top of the American middle class."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 450297.0,
      "end_time": 453179.0,
      "text": "His counterpart is not college-educated"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 453179.0,
      "end_time": 456243.0,
      "text": "and works as a laborer, works as a clerk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 456243.0,
      "end_time": 459555.0,
      "text": "does low-level white collar or blue collar work in the economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 459555.0,
      "end_time": 461960.0,
      "text": "We're going to call that guy \"Bill.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 461960.0,
      "end_time": 464039.0,
      "text": "And if you go back about 50 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 464039.0,
      "end_time": 467856.0,
      "text": "Bill and Ted were leading remarkably similar lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 467856.0,
      "end_time": 470359.0,
      "text": "For example, in 1960 they were both very likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 470359.0,
      "end_time": 473729.0,
      "text": "to have full-time jobs, working at least 40 hours a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 473729.0,
      "end_time": 477025.0,
      "text": "But as the social researcher Charles Murray has documented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 477025.0,
      "end_time": 479993.0,
      "text": "as we started to automate the economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 479993.0,
      "end_time": 484140.0,
      "text": "and 1960 is just about when computers started to be used by businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 484140.0,
      "end_time": 487011.0,
      "text": "as we started to progressively inject technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 487011.0,
      "end_time": 489747.0,
      "text": "and automation and digital stuff into the economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 489747.0,
      "end_time": 492772.0,
      "text": "the fortunes of Bill and Ted diverged a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 492772.0,
      "end_time": 494891.0,
      "text": "Over this time frame, Ted has continued"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 494891.0,
      "end_time": 497643.0,
      "text": "to hold a full-time job. Bill hasn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 497643.0,
      "end_time": 501914.0,
      "text": "In many cases, Bill has left the economy entirely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 501914.0,
      "end_time": 504178.0,
      "text": "and Ted very rarely has."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 504178.0,
      "end_time": 507443.0,
      "text": "Over time, Ted's marriage has stayed quite happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 507443.0,
      "end_time": 509084.0,
      "text": "Bill's hasn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 509084.0,
      "end_time": 512406.0,
      "text": "And Ted's kids have grown up in a two-parent home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 512405.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515625.99999999994,
      "text": "while Bill's absolutely have not over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 515626.0,
      "end_time": 518030.0,
      "text": "Other ways that Bill is dropping out of society?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 518030.0,
      "end_time": 521719.0,
      "text": "He's decreased his voting in presidential elections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 521719.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525712.0,
      "text": "and he's started to go to prison a lot more often."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 525712.0,
      "end_time": 529696.0,
      "text": "So I cannot tell a happy story about these social trends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 529696.0,
      "end_time": 532443.0,
      "text": "and they don't show any signs of reversing themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 532443.0,
      "end_time": 535416.0,
      "text": "They're also true no matter which ethnic group"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 535416.0,
      "end_time": 537137.0,
      "text": "or demographic group we look at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 537137.0,
      "end_time": 539213.0,
      "text": "and they're actually getting so severe"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 539213.0,
      "end_time": 540984.0,
      "text": "that they're in danger of overwhelming"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 540984.0,
      "end_time": 544632.0,
      "text": "even the amazing progress we made with the Civil Rights Movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 544632.0,
      "end_time": 547144.0,
      "text": "And what my friends in Silicon Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 547144.0,
      "end_time": 552395.0,
      "text": "and Cambridge are overlooking is that they're Ted."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 552395.0,
      "end_time": 555832.0,
      "text": "They're living these amazingly busy, productive lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 555832.0,
      "end_time": 558222.0,
      "text": "and they've got all the benefits to show from that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 558222.0,
      "end_time": 560657.0,
      "text": "while Bill is leading a very different life."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 560657.0,
      "end_time": 562797.0,
      "text": "They're actually both proof of how right Voltaire was"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 562797.0,
      "end_time": 565049.0,
      "text": "when he talked about the benefits of work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 565049.0,
      "end_time": 568630.0,
      "text": "and the fact that it saves us from not one but three great evils."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 568630.0,
      "end_time": 569627.0,
      "text": "[\"Work saves a man from three great evils: boredom, vice and need.\" â€” Voltaire]"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 569627.0,
      "end_time": 572963.0,
      "text": "So with these challenges, what do we do about them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 572963.0,
      "end_time": 575546.0,
      "text": "The economic playbook is surprisingly clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 575546.0,
      "end_time": 578686.0,
      "text": "surprisingly straightforward, in the short term especially."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 578686.0,
      "end_time": 581578.0,
      "text": "The robots are not going to take all of our jobs in the next year or two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 581578.0,
      "end_time": 586046.0,
      "text": "so the classic Econ 101 playbook is going to work just fine:"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 586046.0,
      "end_time": 588198.0,
      "text": "Encourage entrepreneurship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 588198.0,
      "end_time": 590394.0,
      "text": "double down on infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 590394.0,
      "end_time": 592093.0,
      "text": "and make sure we're turning out people"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 592093.0,
      "end_time": 595690.0,
      "text": "from our educational system with the appropriate skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 595690.0,
      "end_time": 598967.0,
      "text": "But over the longer term, if we are moving into an economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 598967.0,
      "end_time": 601619.0,
      "text": "that's heavy on technology and light on labor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 601619.0,
      "end_time": 604047.0,
      "text": "and we are, then we have to consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 604047.0,
      "end_time": 605831.0,
      "text": "some more radical interventions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 605831.0,
      "end_time": 609030.0,
      "text": "for example, something like a guaranteed minimum income."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 609030.0,
      "end_time": 612742.0,
      "text": "Now, that's probably making some folk in this room uncomfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 612742.0,
      "end_time": 616599.0,
      "text": "because that idea is associated with the extreme left wing"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 616599.0,
      "end_time": 619818.0,
      "text": "and with fairly radical schemes for redistributing wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 619818.0,
      "end_time": 621771.0,
      "text": "I did a little bit of research on this notion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 621771.0,
      "end_time": 624226.0,
      "text": "and it might calm some folk down to know that"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 624226.0,
      "end_time": 626858.0,
      "text": "the idea of a net guaranteed minimum income"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 626858.0,
      "end_time": 630020.0,
      "text": "has been championed by those frothing-at-the-mouth socialists"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 630035.0,
      "end_time": 635508.0,
      "text": "Friedrich Hayek, Richard Nixon and Milton Friedman."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 635508.0,
      "end_time": 637387.0,
      "text": "And if you find yourself worried"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 637387.0,
      "end_time": 640696.0,
      "text": "that something like a guaranteed income"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 640696.0,
      "end_time": 642971.0,
      "text": "is going to stifle our drive to succeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 642971.0,
      "end_time": 644735.0,
      "text": "and make us kind of complacent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 644735.0,
      "end_time": 647525.0,
      "text": "you might be interested to know that social mobility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 647525.0,
      "end_time": 650200.0,
      "text": "one of the things we really pride ourselves on in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 650200.0,
      "end_time": 653540.0,
      "text": "is now lower than it is in the northern European countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 653540.0,
      "end_time": 656739.0,
      "text": "that have these very generous social safety nets."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 656739.0,
      "end_time": 659531.0,
      "text": "So the economic playbook is actually pretty straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 659531.0,
      "end_time": 662587.0,
      "text": "The societal one is a lot more challenging."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 662587.0,
      "end_time": 664735.0,
      "text": "I don't know what the playbook is"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 664735.0,
      "end_time": 668563.0,
      "text": "for getting Bill to engage and stay engaged throughout life."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 668563.0,
      "end_time": 671067.0,
      "text": "I do know that education is a huge part of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 671067.0,
      "end_time": 672847.0,
      "text": "I witnessed this firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 672847.0,
      "end_time": 676603.0,
      "text": "I was a Montessori kid for the first few years of my education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 676603.0,
      "end_time": 678132.0,
      "text": "and what that education taught me"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 678132.0,
      "end_time": 680223.0,
      "text": "is that the world is an interesting place"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 680223.0,
      "end_time": 682864.0,
      "text": "and my job is to go explore it."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 682864.0,
      "end_time": 684565.0,
      "text": "The school stopped in third grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 684565.0,
      "end_time": 686633.0,
      "text": "so then I entered the public school system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 686633.0,
      "end_time": 690999.0,
      "text": "and it felt like I had been sent to the Gulag."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 690999.0,
      "end_time": 693900.0,
      "text": "With the benefit of hindsight, I now know the job"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 693900.0,
      "end_time": 696414.0,
      "text": "was to prepare me for life as a clerk or a laborer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 696414.0,
      "end_time": 698744.0,
      "text": "but at the time it felt like the job was to kind of"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 698744.0,
      "end_time": 702568.0,
      "text": "bore me into some submission with what was going on around me."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 702568.0,
      "end_time": 703916.0,
      "text": "We have to do better than this."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 703916.0,
      "end_time": 707592.0,
      "text": "We cannot keep turning out Bills."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 707592.0,
      "end_time": 709936.0,
      "text": "So we see some green shoots that things are getting better."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 709936.0,
      "end_time": 712760.0,
      "text": "We see technology deeply impacting education"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 712760.0,
      "end_time": 715288.0,
      "text": "and engaging people, from our youngest learners"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 715288.0,
      "end_time": 717052.0,
      "text": "up to our oldest ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 717052.0,
      "end_time": 719672.0,
      "text": "We see very prominent business voices telling us"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 719672.0,
      "end_time": 722888.0,
      "text": "we need to rethink some of the things that we've been holding dear for a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 722888.0,
      "end_time": 725148.0,
      "text": "And we see very serious and sustained"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 725148.0,
      "end_time": 727952.0,
      "text": "and data-driven efforts to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 727952.0,
      "end_time": 731495.0,
      "text": "how to intervene in some of the most troubled communities that we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 731495.0,
      "end_time": 733704.0,
      "text": "So the green shoots are out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 733704.0,
      "end_time": 735138.0,
      "text": "I don't want to pretend for a minute"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 735138.0,
      "end_time": 737080.0,
      "text": "that what we have is going to be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 737080.0,
      "end_time": 739222.0,
      "text": "We're facing very tough challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 739222.0,
      "end_time": 742328.0,
      "text": "To give just one example, there are about five million Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 742328.0,
      "end_time": 745142.0,
      "text": "who have been unemployed for at least six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 745142.0,
      "end_time": 746484.0,
      "text": "We're not going to fix things for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 746484.0,
      "end_time": 748927.0,
      "text": "by sending them back to Montessori."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 748927.0,
      "end_time": 751282.0,
      "text": "And my biggest worry is that we're creating a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 751282.0,
      "end_time": 753831.0,
      "text": "where we're going to have glittering technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 753831.0,
      "end_time": 756136.0,
      "text": "embedded in kind of a shabby society"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 756136.0,
      "end_time": 759103.0,
      "text": "and supported by an economy that generates inequality"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 759103.0,
      "end_time": 760584.0,
      "text": "instead of opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 760584.0,
      "end_time": 763336.0,
      "text": "But I actually don't think that's what we're going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 763336.0,
      "end_time": 764965.0,
      "text": "I think we're going to do something a lot better"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 764965.0,
      "end_time": 767075.0,
      "text": "for one very straightforward reason:"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 767075.0,
      "end_time": 769043.0,
      "text": "The facts are getting out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 769043.0,
      "end_time": 771085.0,
      "text": "The realities of this new machine age"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 771085.0,
      "end_time": 774400.0,
      "text": "and the change in the economy are becoming more widely known."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 774400.0,
      "end_time": 777251.0,
      "text": "If we wanted to accelerate that process, we could do things"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 777251.0,
      "end_time": 780017.0,
      "text": "like have our best economists and policymakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 780017.0,
      "end_time": 782436.0,
      "text": "play \"Jeopardy!\" against Watson."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 782436.0,
      "end_time": 785986.0,
      "text": "We could send Congress on an autonomous car road trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 785986.0,
      "end_time": 787639.0,
      "text": "And if we do enough of these kinds of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 787639.0,
      "end_time": 791043.0,
      "text": "the awareness is going to sink in that things are going to be different."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 791043.0,
      "end_time": 792814.0,
      "text": "And then we're off to the races,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 792814.0,
      "end_time": 795244.0,
      "text": "because I don't believe for a second"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 795244.0,
      "end_time": 798212.0,
      "text": "that we have forgotten how to solve tough challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 798212.0,
      "end_time": 802562.0,
      "text": "or that we have become too apathetic or hard-hearted to even try."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 802562.0,
      "end_time": 804956.0,
      "text": "I started my talk with quotes from wordsmiths"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 804956.0,
      "end_time": 807772.0,
      "text": "who were separated by an ocean and a century."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 807772.0,
      "end_time": 809924.0,
      "text": "Let me end it with words from politicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 809924.0,
      "end_time": 811655.0,
      "text": "who were similarly distant."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 811655.0,
      "end_time": 814988.0,
      "text": "Winston Churchill came to my home of MIT in 1949,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 814988.0,
      "end_time": 817136.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"If we are to bring the broad masses"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 817136.0,
      "end_time": 820846.0,
      "text": "of the people in every land to the table of abundance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 820846.0,
      "end_time": 823876.0,
      "text": "it can only be by the tireless improvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 823876.0,
      "end_time": 826849.0,
      "text": "of all of our means of technical production.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 826849.0,
      "end_time": 829468.0,
      "text": "Abraham Lincoln realized there was one other ingredient."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 829468.0,
      "end_time": 832366.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I am a firm believer in the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 832366.0,
      "end_time": 834699.0,
      "text": "If given the truth, they can be depended upon"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 834699.0,
      "end_time": 837068.0,
      "text": "to meet any national crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 837068.0,
      "end_time": 839852.0,
      "text": "The great point is to give them the plain facts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 839852.0,
      "end_time": 842962.0,
      "text": "So the optimistic note, great point that I want to leave you with"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 842962.0,
      "end_time": 846107.0,
      "text": "is that the plain facts of the machine age are becoming clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 846107.0,
      "end_time": 848564.0,
      "text": "and I have every confidence that we're going to use them"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 848564.0,
      "end_time": 851479.0,
      "text": "to chart a good course into the challenging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 851479.0,
      "end_time": 854012.0,
      "text": "abundant economy that we're creating."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 854012.0,
      "end_time": 855703.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 855703.0,
      "end_time": 860085.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}